condition.narrative: Finance Agreement :Business Development Agreements | Description :To carry out Component 2.1 of the Project, the Recipient, throughthe Project Coordination Unit, shall make In-Kind Capital Grants to eligible Entrepreneurs under a Business Development Agreementon terms and conditions approved by the Association, in accordance with eligibility criteria and procedures acceptable to theAssociation as further described in the Project Implementation Manual. | Frequency :CONTINUOUS

Finance Agreement :Creation and Maintenance of Steering Committee and Project Coordination Unit | Description :Create within onemonth of the Effective Date, and thereafter maintain (1) the Steering Committee to provide oversight for the Project; and (2) theProject Coordination Unit in charge of the day-to-day fiduciary management and coordination of the Project. | Frequency :CONTINUOUS
